%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Pre-existing or Recurring Cancer are not eligible for sharing.
Name: Cancer Limitations

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: If a Member was diagnosed, or treatment was received, for Cancer within 5 years of the Member effective date, Cancer expenses are Not Eligible for Sharing
Name: Cancer Look Back Period

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Lupus, Lyme Disease, Macular Degeneration (wet or dry), Morbid Obesity (pending weight loss), Multiple Sclerosis, Muscular Dystrophy, Parkinson’s Disease, Sickle-Cell Disease, Spina Bifida, Typhoid.
Name: Lifetime Pre-existing Condition Exclusion

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Lifetime Pre-Existing Condition Exclusion applies to named conditions. Please refer to Member Guidelines for the conditions not eligible for sharing. Pre-Existing Limitations do not apply to Outpatient Specialist or Primary Care Physician Office Visits.
Name: Lifetime Pre-existing Condition Exclusion

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Alzheimer’s ,Aneurysm, Autism Spectrum Disorders, Cerebral Palsy n Pulmonary Disease (COPD), Cystic Fibrosis, Dementia, Diabetes Type I, Down’s Syndrome, Ectasia, Emphysema, Fragile X Syndrome, Fibromyalgia, Hepatitis (Chronic Viral B & C), HIV/AIDS,
Name: Lifetime Pre-existing Condition Exclusion

%vlocity_namespace%__AttributeDisplayNam: Medical Expenses that exceed a stated Maximum
%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Any amount exceeding a stated  Maximum will be the Member responsibility.
Name: Medical Expenses that exceed a stated Maximum

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Sharing for medical services will not be available when the condition  is shown to be the result of medical non-compliance with the Physician's recommended care, treatment or advice.
Name: Medical Non-Compliance

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: If a medical need is related to a diagnosis, treatment or procedure that is ineligible for sharing in any way, that medical need is Not Eligible for Sharing. Refer to Information Packet for services not Eligible for sharing
Name: Not eligible for sharing

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Any sickness or injury for which a Member received medical treatment, advice, care or services including diagnostic measures, took prescribed drugs or showed signs or symptoms, whether treated or not, within 24 months of Member's program effective date.
Name: Pre-Existing Condition 24/24: Definition

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Eligibility for a Pre-Existing Condition has a 24 month waiting period. Pre-Existing Limitations do not apply to Outpatient Specialist or Primary Care Physician Office Visits.
Name: Pre-Existing Condition 24/24: Eligibililty

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Tobacco Use: If a Member used or uses tobacco in any form, (this includes vaping of any nicotine products), any health-related issues are Not Eligible for Sharing.
Name: Tobacco Use

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Visit Fees do not apply to ISA and ISR and applies after the Member’s ISA is met.
Name: Visit Fees
